[[include info:end]]

This is a generic Sigma-10 Dark Mode Theme. It can be used for any purpose. To use this theme on an article, use the following code:

> @@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:dark]]@@

+ Theme Examples

How various page elements look while using this theme follow below.

